## Push Summary — skrptiq-cli (main)

### What shipped
General scrolling for all output — not just /list:

- **pgup/pgdown and shift+up/down** scroll through all session output, always available regardless of autocomplete state
- **Scroll indicator** shows "↑ scroll — 45% pgup/pgdown to navigate" when there's content above the viewport
- **Smart auto-scroll** — new output only auto-scrolls to bottom if you're already at the bottom. If you've scrolled up to read, it stays put.
- **/list** output sorted by type then name alphabetically
